Quick setup: (copy-paste to terminal)

    git clone --no-checkout https://github.com/ipwnponies/dotfiles.git tmp-dotfiles
    mv tmp-dotfiles/.git .
    rmdir tmp-dotfiles
    git checkout  -f
    git submodule update --init


Install a vim plugin:

    git submodule add https://github.com/tpope/vim-sensible.git .vim/bundle/vim-sensible
